description: Womens Compression Socks by Sugar Free Sox

Sugar Free Sox Compression Socks include a microfiber fabric that is soft to the touch, has great durability, and ultimate stay up power.  These socks enhance circulation and keep your legs healthier.   Compression socks are ideal for people with varicose veins, edema, swollen legs/ankles/feet, plantar fasciitis, or circulatory problems.   The refined and extended toe construction leaves room for toes to move around and avoid tightness and discomfort.   The 15-20 MMHG of graduated moderate compression keeps legs energized and increases circulation.
Enjoy the super comfort of Sugar Free Sox and keep your legs feeling and looking healthy!
Fits women's shoe sizes 7-10.5, Knee High Length
